    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 58-61.</p><p>Slayer’s Mark</p><p>Also at 22nd level, you learn to tag your quarry with a deadly mark. As a bonus action, you can expend 1 Legendary Point to hone your senses on a creature within 500 feet. Your critical range against that creature is increased by 1 and you have advantage on attack rolls against it. You always know the creature’s location while in the same plane of existence as you. The mark remains for 8 hours, or until you mark another creature.</p></div>",
